Text: I have not yet read the book but I have scanned it and made some mental notes about how the system works. I decided to try it out on my wife just to see what would happen. I can see this saving some marriages and yeah getting a lot of dudes laid. Now I have to go back and actually study this material and apply it with focus and then we shall see the results. I expect it will work the way it is intended. I will be seeding this tenfold.
